OL,3,CHomeless support charity fears people
OL,4,Cwill die on the streets this winter
OL,6,FAn organisation working with the
OL,7,Fhomeless in Belfast has said it fears
OL,8,Fpeople will die on the streets this
OL,9,Fwinter.
OL,11,FPeople's Kitchen has called for a
OL,12,Fdiscussion around how the Housing
OL,13,FExecutive responds to extreme weather.
OL,15,FThe Housing Executive maintains its
OL,16,FSevere Weather Emergency Protocol is
OL,17,Fproactively enacted when necessary and
OL,18,Fforms part of a coordinated approach.
