OL,3,CHomeless support charity fears people
OL,4,Cwill die on the streets this winter
OL,6,FPaul McKusker from The People's
OL,7,FKitchen said: "There is a meeting next
OL,8,Fweek with all the agencies organised
OL,9,Fby Homeless Connect.
OL,11,F"I think at that meeting we need to be
OL,12,Fvery clear moving forward to ensure
OL,13,Fthe parameters around the Severe
OL,14,FWeather Emergency Protocol are looked
OL,15,Fand to ensure that additional beds can
OL,16,Fbe made available in any emergency in
OL,17,Fthe city if we need people off the
OL,18,Fstreets.
