OL,3,CHomeless support charity fears people
OL,4,Cwill die on the streets this winter
OL,6,F"It is going to get colder over winter
OL,7,Fthe next few months and people are at
OL,8,Frisk of dying on the streets."
OL,10,FJohn and Kenzie know what life on the
OL,11,Fstreets is like. They spent several
OL,12,Fmonths in a tent in Belfast city
OL,13,Fcentre.
OL,15,F"We were thankfully staying on the
OL,16,Fstreets when it was not as cold, it
OL,17,Fwas summer and we were warm enough.
