OL,3,CHomeless support charity fears people
OL,4,Cwill die on the streets this winter
OL,6,F"The people on the streets now we
OL,7,Fwould love to just try and help them
OL,8,Fbecause it is freezing cold and we
OL,9,Fknow what it is like. It is scary.
OL,11,F"We were luck we had a tent, these
OL,12,Fpeople don't. These people are
OL,13,Factually lying on the bare floor",
OL,14,FKenzie said.
OL,16,FJohn added: "We were lucky that we had
OL,17,Feachother. We were able to push
OL,18,Feachother through it."
