OL,6,FIn a statement the Housing Executive
OL,7,Fsaid: "The implementation of this
OL,8,Fprotocol is not a statutory duty and
OL,9,Fwe proactively enact the protocol when
OL,10,Fit is necessary.
OL,12,F"We routinely monitor weather
OL,13,Fconditions, including all warnings
OL,14,Fissued by the Met Office, as part of
OL,15,Four planning for the implementation of
OL,16,Fa SWEP.
