OL,3,CHomeless support charity fears people
OL,4,Cwill die on the streets this winter
OL,6,F"Each decision is a result of a
OL,7,Fcoordinated approach within the
OL,8,FHousing Executive, supported by a
OL,9,Frange of partners who provide
OL,10,Fadditional emergency accommodation.
OL,12,F"These are regulated and experienced
OL,13,Forganisations and have been working
OL,14,Fextremely hard to meet a growing
OL,15,Fdemand for their services."
OL,17,FJohn and Kenzie are now in a hostel
OL,18,Ftheir hope is that by next Christmas
OL,19,Fthey will be in a new home.
